About life in the Last Shelter
#show Glav
#show Hero
#CAMERA 3 30 3 1.5
#phrase Glav  1
The Last Shelter is ready to take anybody who comes with open heart and  a clear soul. We do not ask who you are or where you are from, what was in your past or what you expect from the future.
#phrase Glav  2
Particularly since some of our brethren do not remember their past, so it would be useless to ask. For example, brother Blondie - he came here after he got away from Death Canyon, and he left via the portal leading to the Useless Lands.
#phrase Glav  3
Yes, oh brother Blondie was a truly unusual man! He was never afraid of open combat with guards, and would stab enemies in the back with the greatest of pleasure ...
#phrase Glav  4
But enough of him. If you live in the past you will not move into the future!
